com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.importer.rf2

Class SnomedCompositeImporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.importer.AbstractLoggingImporter
      • com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.importer.rf2.SnomedCompositeImporter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Importer

    public class SnomedCompositeImporter
extends AbstractLoggingImporter
    A composite importer that coordinates the operation of its child importers:
    • runs all pre-import steps are in order
    • gathers units from all nested importers
    • reorders units are according to the specified ordering
    • carries out the import on the nested units
    • runs all post-import steps in order
